headline.print_headline: Bombs Targeting Soldiers, Shoppers Kill 16 in Iraq
headline.main: Bombs Targeting Soldiers, Shoppers Kill 16 in Iraq

lead_paragraph: Attacks across Iraq, including a series of bombings targeting shoppers in a Sunni neighborhood in the country's capital, killed at least 16 people Saturday, authorities said.
